      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "4950-5006",
      "markText": "母亲完全没有主见；她这漫长的一生，虽然优雅温柔，但一直异常顺从——典型的附属品。她甚至被认为没有脑子为自己做主。",
      "totalCount": 732,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300036415&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4950&rangeEnd=5006",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b8f320e0813ab74b9g0157e1?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4950&rangeEnd=5006"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300036415_4_44428-44457",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "44428-44457",
      "markText": "如此心照不宣、相互体谅的小小善举令他俩的关系愈发亲密无间。",
      "totalCount": 720,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300036415&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=44428&rangeEnd=44457",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b8f320e0813ab74b9g0157e1?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=44428&rangeEnd=44457"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300036415_4_3296-3331",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3296-3331",
      "markText": "死神竟然成了召集者，仿佛所有生者即刻前来赴约，是为寻求保护和相互支持。",
      "totalCount": 715,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300036415&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3296&rangeEnd=3331",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b8f320e0813ab74b9g0157e1?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3296&rangeEnd=3331"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300036415_5_10045-10102",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "10045-10102",
      "markText": "他有意无意地试着用一条条毯子、一块块垫子，熄灭她内心的憧憬与渴望，犹如将一颗破碎的心灵置于一床羽毛褥垫，哄其入眠。",
      "totalCount": 714,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300036415&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=10045&rangeEnd=10102",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b8f320e0813ab74b9g0157e1?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=10045&rangeEnd=10102"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300036415_4_7989-8062",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "7989-8062",
      "markText": "母亲余生失去了唯一的生活意义，多半过得凄惨，我觉得在这几年里，尽力照顾好她应当是我们所有人的快乐和荣幸。负担这个词，我觉得，可真不合适，伊迪丝。”",
      "totalCount": 702,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300036415&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=7989&rangeEnd=8062",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b8f320e0813ab74b9g0157e1?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=7989&rangeEnd=8062"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300036415_4_15494-15572",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "15494-15572",
      "markText": "母亲的人生破碎了，但她的情绪一直很稳定，在她独自默默承受一切的时候，我们定要好好庇护她，其他必须安排的事务乃至与外界联络的任务应当都由她能干的子女们来承担。",
      "totalCount": 702,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300036415&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=15494&rangeEnd=15572",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b8f320e0813ab74b9g0157e1?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=15494&rangeEnd=15572"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300036415_4_30279-30331",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "30279-30331",
      "markText": "彻底安逸之日到来前，切勿肆意回忆；纵情享受之前，切勿放纵欢愉。眼前零星的期待切不可糟蹋了之后的快乐盛宴。",
      "totalCount": 676,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300036415&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=30279&rangeEnd=30331",
