      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300036415&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=8669&rangeEnd=8720",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b8f320e0813ab74b9g0157e1?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=8669&rangeEnd=8720"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300036415_6_7016-7098",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "7016-7098",
      "markText": "她不知被什么给撞上了，好似废弃许久的教堂里的破钟又重新被敲响，空谷里并未传来动人的乐曲，但寂寥的教堂内回声四起，响彻天际，惊动了巢里的椋鸟，震得蜘蛛网也颤动了起来。",
      "totalCount": 585,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300036415&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7016&rangeEnd=7098",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b8f320e0813ab74b9g0157e1?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7016&rangeEnd=7098"
